data.description: Tucked alongside the San Antonio suburb of Boerne, Texas - River Rock Ranch provides the desirable Texas Hill Country lifestyle that many home buyers seek. Residents can enjoy the ample amenities that River Rock Ranch offers. In addition to the guarded entry gate, residents have access to a resort-style swimming pool with a lazy river, top of the line fitness center, expansive clubhouse, children's playground, and so much more. The exclusive living that River Rock Ranch provides also boast panoramic wooded vistas and stunning views. The vibes of renowned Hill Country abound of a serene sense of living with live oaks amidst the landscape, tranquil surroundings, and views that are breath taking. Located off Boerne Stage Road, River Rock Ranch allows easy access to IH-10 and Loop 1604. This desirable location offers residents a quick commute to major employers and South Texas Medical Center. Additionally, both La Cantera and The Rim shopping centers provide ample dining, shopping and entertainment less than 10 miles away. Fair Oaks Ranch Golf Club and Palmer Course at La Cantera can also be found within just a few minutes of River Rock Ranch. In addition to golf, other attractions such as Leon Springs and Six Flags are super convenient destinations, as well as the quaint town of Boerne. Children living in River Rock Ranch attend schools within the Northside Independent School District, a quality public education system known for its longstanding excellence. Northside ISD include these highly acclaimed schools for River Rock Ranch students: Sara B. McAndrew Elementary, Ed Rawlinson Middle School, and Tom C. Clark High School.
